1
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:46,319
Miss Yan, what is this?

2
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:48,959
It's a special breakfast for Mr. Wei'an.

3
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:49,959
Please,

4
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,959
help yourself.

5
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:59,400
Are you sure this is edible?

6
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,640
Don't worry. 120 will be here soon.

7
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,639
You give me a gift,

8
00:02:13,639 --> 00:02:15,439
and I'll finish our business

9
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:17,639
after you finish this meal.

10
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:22,080
What business?

11
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,080
Why so mysterious?

12
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,879
When are you going to change the ending?

13
00:02:26,439 --> 00:02:27,439
Uh...

14
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:28,759
Well,

15
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,759
I think there's something more important

16
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:33,120
than this.

17
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:33,719
I don't think

18
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:36,280
anything is more important than this.

19
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:45,639
How about

20
00:02:46,439 --> 00:02:47,319
I keep it a secret for you?

21
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:49,599
Let's give him a surprise together.

22
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,000
What are you two doing there?

23
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,800
Do you need to talk inside?

24
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:56,159
I'm showing Mr. Weian around.

25
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:57,080
Not finished yet.

26
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:57,840
Yeah, we're showing him around.

27
00:02:58,759 --> 00:02:59,120
Let's go.

28
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:04,560
Come here.

29
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:05,479
Closer to me.

30
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,360
Are you sure you want to do it yourself?

31
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,520
Of course.

32
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:14,080
Here.

33
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,080
Try this.

34
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:20,840
Have a taste.

35
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:24,520
Hmm.

36
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:25,719
How does it taste?

37
00:03:26,639 --> 00:03:28,479
This is Xu Chi's favorite sweet and sour flavor.

38
00:03:28,719 --> 00:03:29,479
It's quite delicious.

39
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:31,000
Come on.

40
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:31,919
Now beat an egg.

41
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:42,120
Yeah, that's about right.

42
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,439
Like this?

43
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:46,879
Make sure to beat it evenly.

44
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:48,360
In one direction.

45
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:48,680
Like this.

46
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:48,919
Okay.

47
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:53,000
It'll start to foam up slowly.

48
00:03:54,319 --> 00:03:55,599
Xu Chi is very picky about this.

49
00:03:55,599 --> 00:03:56,039
Oh.

50
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,879
First, slice the carrot into thin pieces.

51
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:09,719
There's such detailed work?

52
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:10,520
I'll help you.

53
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,000
Right.

54
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:15,879
Cut.

55
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,519
What are you doing?

56
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:17,480
Do you need to teach me?

57
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:18,279
I can teach you too.

58
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:20,800
Oh, my.

59
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:22,879
You can go out first.

60
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,279
We're not done yet.

61
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,000
Wei'an taught me well.

62
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,279
What can he teach that I can't?

63
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:32,720
I can't say.

64
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,600
This is our little secret.

65
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,600
Okay.

66
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:37,879
Yan Ying, come here.

67
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:40,759
What are you doing?

68
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:43,800
I can't tell you now,

69
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,399
but it's very important to me.

70
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,839
I made an appointment with Mr. Wei'an.

71
00:04:48,279 --> 00:04:49,399
Wei'an, Wei'an.

72
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:50,720
Is Wei'an the only thing on your mind?

73
00:04:50,879 --> 00:04:51,279
Yes.

74
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:52,879
The reason I'm here

75
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:53,920
is Wei'an.

76
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,399
Strange.

77
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:16,720
Why is he so angry?

78
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,240
When you know him better,

79
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,800
you'll know.

80
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:44,959
Where is Xu Chi?

81
00:05:45,399 --> 00:05:46,759
Why hasn't he come back yet?

82
00:05:49,879 --> 00:05:51,199
Didn't you two have a fight?

83
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:53,639
Miss Yan still cares about him so much?

84
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:58,680
You were deliberately close to me when you taught me to make cakes this morning.

85
00:05:59,279 --> 00:06:00,600
It was to provoke Xu Chi, right?

86
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:06,360
I like talking to smart people.

87
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:08,480
Look.

88
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,600
There's something wrong

89
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,519
with our relationship.

90
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,920
But it seems that

91
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:15,800
there's something wrong with your relationship with him.

92
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,959
is because of Wei'an?

93
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:25,959
Oh.

94
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,680
It's me.

95
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:33,079
I'll find the answer

96
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:35,079
to the problem between Xu Chi and me.

97
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,360
Mr. Wei'an,

98
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,439
you've been to many places, right?

99
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,319
Have you heard of Wangchuan?

100
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:50,839
Wangchuan?

101
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:54,920
Yes.

102
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:56,839
In my hometown,

103
00:06:58,279 --> 00:06:59,560
there is a river

104
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,360
called Wangchuan.

105
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,000
There are many flowers on both sides.

106
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,519
The flowers?

107
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:08,160
I like them.

108
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:09,639
Hey.

109
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,879
Let's play together next time.

110
00:07:12,759 --> 00:07:14,040
One last question.

111
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,000
Where is Xu Chi?
